  /*  
  Installed Extensions:

  ? How to Open settings.json
  * 1 - In your vscode editor, press CTRL + P
  * 2 - Type "settings.json " or ">settings.json"
  * 3 - Enter
  * 4 - Copy and Paste all  this file, you can remove the comments if you want, and change whatever you like.

  !! REQUIRED:
  !! pyxel.min-darkest;
  !! miguelsolorio.fluent-icons;
